news.title: Mysuru civic body's B-khata drive to bring unauthorised properties under tax net
news.para: The civic body aims to bring all 27,616 such properties under the tax net over the next 16 months. This effort is expected to boost property tax revenue.

news.title: Delhi: New sops for vacation of Signature View Apartments for demolition, but no clarity on rent yet
news.para: According to the latest SOPs, May 30 is the deadline for handing over previously vacated flats while July 31 is the final date for the complete vacation and handover of all remaining flats.

news.title: Pool, gym NOCs stuck over new rules, but Noida sports department in no mood to relent
news.para: The move follows inspections by officials of the department after several condominiums decided to open their pools, with the NOCs not coming through.

news.title: Karnataka RERA, just a paper tiger: Home buyers
news.para: K-RERA data reveals that of the 1,660 recovery orders issued involving `758.85 crore, only 233 cases have seen action, resulting in a recovery of `91.88 crore.

news.title: Panvel: 96 Pioneer CHS flat owners get eviction notices as building fails to obtain OC
news.para: The corporation recently discontinued their water tanker service, which was being provided free of cost since November 2023, resulting in accumulated costs of Rs 18.54 lakh, despite recurring water tax payment defaults.

news.title: Seal illegal structures even if notices issued: Telangana HC to GHMC
news.para: Justice B Vijaysen Reddy passed this interim order while hearing petition filed by Jijjuvarapu Ramesh who brought to the court's notice one such flagrant violation in OU Colony, Shaikpet wherein a person took permission from GHMC to construct stilt plus two floors but went on raising more floors.

news.title: Mumbai builder gets stop-work notice as residents flag shrinking Walkeshwar Road
news.para: The April 26 notice served to architect Preeti Kashyap Barai and developer Dilip Chunilal Chandan pointed out unauthorised erection of building/execution of work at a plot on the road.

news.title: Bokaro deputy commissioner reviews PMAY-U scheme
news.para: Bokaro deputy commissioner (DC) Vijaya Jadhav instructed wide publicity to invite applications from eligible beneficiaries.

news.title: New housing projects to be launched soon in 12 districts of Uttar Pradesh
news.para: "The CM was informed that under the Mukhyamantri Urban Expansion/New City Promotion Scheme, the approved projects will be launched in phases between June and December 2025," an official statement said.

news.title: Delhi HC seeks CBI reply on plea to probe corruption allegations in shopping mall's operations
news.para: ​Justice Girish Kathpalia issued notice to the Central Bureau of Investigation (CBI) on the petition which also sought registration of an FIR under the provisions of the Prevention of Corruption Act and the criminal penal law.

news.title: Nagpur: HC orders demolition of encroachment on road, fines developer
news.para: The court found that despite the society's undertaking in 2019 to remove the encroachments, it failed to act, in violation of prior directives and land-use laws.

news.title: Dawat-e-Hadiyah buys 'Killick House' in South Mumbai for over Rs 72 crore
news.para: The trust has bought the leasehold and ownership rights of the building on Hornby Road from Nippon Investment and Finance Company that was previously part of the Videocon Group and functioned as a promoter group entity for Videocon Industries.

news.title: Nagpur civic body sells 1.25 lakh sq ft plot for Rs 235 crore
news.para: The plot is set to be developed into a premium commercial complex. The deal not only sets a new benchmark for Nagpur's real estate market but also highlights the growing commercial appeal of Orange City Street corridor.

news.title: Bengaluru development body increases tax on its properties by 20% to 45%
news.para: Over 1.2 lakh property owners protest poor roads, irregular water supply, and power issues that continue to plague several BDA layouts across the city

news.title: Maharashtra approves ownership transfer of 28 PMC, PCMC land parcels to Maha Metro
news.para: This move will grant Maharashtra Metro Rail Corporation Limited (Maha Metro) full ownership of the plots, enabling them to commercially develop the properties and boost non-fare box revenue.

news.title: Delhi: DDA razes illegal farmhouses on encroached land in Sainik Farms
news.para: According to officials, the illegal structures had been under development for a long time and were part of a broader trend of unauthorised land use in the area.

news.title: NGT issues notice to TDI City over non-functional STPs, water pollution
news.para: ​​This action follows findings submitted by a joint committee formed by the NGT to investigate complaints about untreated wastewater and water stagnation in the area.

news.title: YEIDA to launch portal for over 4,500 homebuyers of Jaiprakash Associates
news.para: A subcommittee of various homebuyers' associations has been set up to represent collective interests and coordinate with YEIDA.

news.title: E-draw for 708 affordable flats will be held again in Gurugram
news.para: ​The decision to scrap the e-draw — announced through a public notice on Thursday (May 1) — came after alleged "technical discrepancies and regional bias" raised serious concerns over the fairness of the process.

news.title: Ghaziabad: Builder digs for basement & damages drain, society flooded
news.para: In Prateek Grand City, residents of the upper floors claimed they were "trapped" in their homes as the maintenance team was forced to shut lifts as putrid water filled the subbasement. The society's 24 towers, each with 28 floors, have nearly 3,000 residents.
